The paper deals with natural language processing tasks and image captioning, which are typically associated with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep reinforcement learning also suggests a connection to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
